title: Dealing with Trauma
itunes:title: Dealing with Trauma
description:
Trauma shapes us into who we are, but we are never really taught how to deal with our trauma. In this episode, I will teach you the best ways to go back and relive old traumas and memories, so that you can let go of them and move forward in your life in a positive way.
